summary: Geochemist/geologist with 13 years industry experience post-PhD. Logical thinker with a keen interest in new geochemical technologies, and applying inorganic/organic geochemistry to solve geological and engineering problems on regional to field scales. Hard working and positive person, with a love for the outdoors, sports, and music.
